---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-brand-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="reveal relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586023492125-27b2c045efd7?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="LinxCosmo lifestyle" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-48 h-48 border border-brand-gold/30 -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-48 h-48 bg-brand-gold/10 -z-10"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p class="text-brand-gold text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-brand-dark leading-tight mb-8">
          A Dynamic<br/>
          <span class="italic text-brand-gray">Innovative Company</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            LinxCosmo &mdash; a dynamic and innovative company dedicated to enhancing everyday life through our unique and creative lifestyle products. At the core of our brand is a vision to connect and unify the myriad elements of modern living, bringing together functionality, style, and sustainability.
          </p>
          <p>
            Founded with the belief that thoughtfully designed products can transform ordinary spaces into extraordinary experiences, we specialize in crafting a diverse range of items for the home, garden, outdoor adventures, pet care, personal protection, sports, and beauty &mdash; all with a commitment to quality and a nod to the natural world.
          </p>
          <p>
            As a company, LinxCosmo is more than just a purveyor of fine goods; we are a community of dreamers, doers, and difference-makers. We believe in the power of creativity to make a positive impact on the world and are committed to using our platform to foster a more connected and vibrant global society.
          </p>
          <p class="italic text-brand-gold">
            Welcome to LinxCosmo &mdash; where every product tells a story and every purchase makes a difference.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-8">
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-gold">50+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray-light mt-1">Product Lines</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px h-12 bg-brand-gold/30"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-gold">10K+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray-light mt-1">Happy Customers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px h-12 bg-brand-gold/30"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-gold">6</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray-light mt-1">Categories</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
